(18, 'Privacy Policy', '', '', 0, 'privacy-policy', 0, '<h6 color:=\"\" hat=\"\" red=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.25; font-size: var(--h6); word-break: break-word; font-family: \">\r\n	&nbsp;</h6>\r\n<div font-size:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth; color: rgb(94, 94, 94); font-family: \" work=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth;\"><span lucida=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: \">At Golden Vacations India, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our website and services. By accessing or using our website, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div font-size:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth; color: rgb(94, 94, 94); font-family: \" work=\"\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div font-size:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth; color: rgb(94, 94, 94); font-family: \" work=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth;\"><span lucida=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scroll-behavior: smooth; font-family: \">Information We Collect:</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div font-size:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: